      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/kitab-al-ghayba-numani:2:14:54",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/14/54",
      "text": [
        ": قلت لأبي عبد الله النداء حق؟ قال: إي والله حتى يسمعه كل قوم بلسانهم. وقال: لا يكون هذا الأمر حتى يذهب تسعة أعشار الناس."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(54) Ahmad bin Muhammad bin Sa’eed narrated from the same previous narrators from Hisham bin Salim that Zurara had said: “Once I asked Abu Abdullah as-Sadiq (as) if the call (from the Heaven) would be true. He said: “Yes, by Allah, until every nation will hear it with its own language.” He also said: “Al-Qa’im will not appear unless nine tenths of people perish.”"
        ]
      }
    },
